---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="about" description="About n0brains.com — think less, ship more.">
  <section class="about-section">
    <h1>about // n0brains</h1>

    <p>
      <strong>n0brains</strong> is a blog for builders who don't overthink.
    </p>

    <p>
      The name says it all. You don't need a perfect plan, a board-approved strategy,
      or a five-year roadmap. You just need to <strong>build</strong>.
    </p>

    <p>
      This site exists because overthinking kills more projects than bad ideas ever will.
      Every post here is something real — a project shipped, a lesson learned,
      a thing that actually works (or spectacularly doesn't).
    </p>

    <p>
      Topics include software engineering, AI agents, crypto trading, and whatever else
      seems worth building. The bar is low. The shipping frequency is high.
    </p>

    <p style="margin-top: 32px; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted);">
      // think less, ship more<br />
      // brain not required
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
